Package gamemechanics

Class Coordinate

java.lang.Object
gamemechanics.Coordinate
public class Coordinate extends Object
Class Coordinate is used for holding the x and y coordinates values on the Board Space 2D array. Will do the move through changing x or y coordinate value Will compare 2 coordinate values will check whether the next intended moving coordinate is blocked
